Class MultiPolygon

java.lang.Object
org.ivoa.dm.caom2.caom2.types.MultiPolygon
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.ivoa.vodml.jpa.JPAManipulations
@Embeddable @VoDml(id="caom2:caom2.types.MultiPolygon", role=dataType) public class MultiPolygon extends Object implements org.ivoa.vodml.jpa.JPAManipulations
a region on the sky defined a sequence of points connected by great-circle segments; each simple polygon is is terminated by a special type of vertex and multiple simple polygons are permitted to describe disconnected regions as a single value. dataType: MultiPolygon
